from bisect import bisect_left

def calculate_walrus_displeasure(n, ages):
    suf = [[10 ** 10, -1] for _ in range(n)]
    suf[-1][0] = ages[-1]
    suf[-1][1] = n + 1
    for i in range(n - 2, -1, -1):
        if suf[i + 1][0] > ages[i]:
            suf[i][0] = ages[i]
            suf[i][1] = i
        else:
            suf[i][0] = suf[i + 1][0]
            suf[i][1] = suf[i + 1][1]
    vals = [i[0] for i in suf]
    displeasure = []
    for i in range(n):
        idx = bisect_left(vals, ages[i])
        displeasure.append(max(-1, idx - i - 2))
    return displeasure
